.SH NOTES
.IX Header "NOTES"
When using the FIPS provider, it is recommended that the
\&\fBconfig_diagnostics\fR option is enabled to prevent accidental use of
non-FIPS validated algorithms via broken or mistaken configuration.
See \fBconfig\fR\|(5).
